  <brief_title>Randomized Clinical Trial in Bellow-the-knee Angioplasty. Treatment of One or More Than One Artery.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Clinical Trial in Bellow-the-knee Angioplasty. Treatment of One or More Than One Artery.</official_title>
