  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It is a randomized study that intend to enroll 80 bellow-the-knee angioplasty procedures in
      which 40 procedures to treat one artery (standart) or more than one artery in the same
      procedure.

      The aim of this study is to know if this strategy increase healing velocity and limb salvage.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
